{"tid":353148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(old news)  Sugar Daddy物質供養 Sugar Baby 男女關係掀糖心風暴","createTime":"2017-08-09T10:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T11:39:24.000Z","uid":95571,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e003c363aff7a3113e50113bd42a0840fe7cdb06","tid":353148,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:42:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20120529/16377999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20120529%2F16377999&d=ZU57oDN5X%2FMBXUiFlfuwvtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=899b5994\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20120529%2F16377999&h=c4795447\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20120529/16377999</a><br />\n<br />\n係咪姐係ptgf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579eaf587b8e2f3054f73cbb2d84e865ad3bc2d5","tid":353148,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"男女關係，有父女關係，有夫妻關係，有情侶關係。美英現時興起新世代男女關係──「糖心爹哋（ Sugar Daddy）與糖心寶貝（ Sugar Baby）」，就是由上年紀的富有男人出錢，「照顧」年輕貌美的女郎。<br />\n<br />\n在糖心爹哋網站開網讓富有男供養大學女生後，「糖心」網站越開越多，有 <a href=\"http://suggardaddyforme.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsuggardaddyforme.com&d=ZU57oDN5X%2FMBXUiFlfuwvtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=ce650794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">suggardaddyforme.com</a>，又有 <a href=\"http://diamonddaddy.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdiamonddaddy.com&d=ZU57oDN5X%2FMBXUiFlfuwvtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=6e0f92cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">diamonddaddy.com</a>等。這些網站聲稱糖心寶貝跟伴遊和娼妓有分別︰「這是一種建立在感情基礎上的交易，非一夜完事。娼妓是你肯出錢就來者不拒，糖心寶貝則可以先試探水溫。」<br />\n有糖心寶貝說，八個月前結交一名糖心爹哋，每次約會都得到數千鎊購物，她則確保糖心爹哋可從壓力中釋放，雙方沒固定關係，又各取所需，那是很美好的時光。另一糖心寶貝說，糖心爹哋未必英俊，但很有內涵，向她做生意提供寶貴意見，所以雙方關係不是一個「錢」字了得。有糖心爹哋則說，錢不是問題，最希望是跟糖心寶貝發展伴侶關係，有人傾訴分擔。<br />\n很明顯，糖心爹哋和糖心寶貝講金講心，但合則來不合則去，雙方沒有約束力。這種關係，糖心網站始祖 <a href=\"http://seekingarrangement.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fseekingarrangement.com&d=ZU57oDN5X%2FMBXUiFlfuwvtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=367ff069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">seekingarrangement.com</a>聲稱很正面，既不會令甜心爹哋與妻子鬧離婚，又讓他們得到宣洩的途徑；而且，40%糖心寶貝是女學生，其次是單親媽媽或希望創業的女性，當中不少人是受到糖心爹哋啟發及資助，成功創立個人生意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以錢換取性愛<br />\n但說穿了，糖心爹哋仍可「以錢和昂貴禮物換取性愛」，只是在日本這叫援交關係，在美歐叫糖心關係。在美歐糖心爹哋越來越多， <a href=\"http://seekingarrangement.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fseekingarrangement.com&d=ZU57oDN5X%2FMBXUiFlfuwvtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=367ff069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">seekingarrangement.com</a>就聲稱福布斯全球富豪榜打入十大的兩人、英國《泰晤士報》富豪榜上有15人，都是他們的糖心爹哋。<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》<br />\n<br />\n被物質蒙蔽　寶貝懊悔<br />\n糖心寶貝由有錢糖心爹哋包養，物質富裕，但隨時迷失利慾當中。五年前曾做糖心寶貝的克羅伊登，以過來人身份，講述被物質關係蒙蔽，一度找不回真愛的懊悔經歷。<br />\n當年29歲的克羅伊登，上網註冊成為糖心寶貝，希望結識成熟聰明能幹的成功男士，但她想不到糖心關係，其實是以糖心爹哋出錢送禮的包養方式運作。她記得自己首次被帶到名店購物的尷尬和貪婪心情，但她很快習以為常，之後更常挑能負擔奢華物質生活的糖心爹哋。但關係建基於物質，克羅伊登覺得糖心關係絕不甜蜜，只覺真愛離自己越來越遠。乍醒的她，花了兩年才能將感情態度帶回正軌，發現愛情比起物質關係，才令心靈更豐盛。<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》"},{"pid":"4a52984faba2aad2c4c92cc7d98fea04ff99e143","tid":353148,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53841b82a4e2e64250d50c3cc27398904b89d79","tid":353148,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"講咁大抽野咪又係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f8a0e0294cac0b694e091667d4acb59aac4373","tid":353148,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講咁大抽野咪又係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a0f1ef8850f2aa14dcf872e2b7f576a1c88d00","tid":353148,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:39:04.000Z","msg":"不嬲Sugar daddy = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfc2263502d78f34560454bafa342c279736276","tid":353148,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲搵Sugar daddy = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}